VGA80x40 Control Register 1Address: #BDE4 or #9FE4Default value: #82This register controls the operation of the VGA80x40 mode.Bit 7  Enable VGA Output        0 = Disabled      1 = EnabledBit 6  Enable Hardware Cursor   0 = Disabled      1 = EnabledBit 5  Hardware Cursor Flash    0 = No Flashing   1 = FlashingBit 4  Hardware Cursor Size     0 = Small         1 = LargeBit 3  Character Attributes     0 = Disabled      1 = EnabledBit 2  Default Foreground Col   0 = No Red        1 = RedBit 1  Default Foreground Col   0 = No Green      1 = GreenBit 0  Default Foreground Col   0 = No Blue       1 = Blue